### Registar um novo utilizador
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "teste2",
  "email": "test2@gmail.com",
  "password": "minhaSenhaSegura"
}

### Obter token de autenticação
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test2@gmail.com",
  "password": "minhaSenhaSegura"
}


### Obter User
GET http://localhost:8080/api/me
content-type: application/json
Authorization: bearer {{token}}

### Apagar User
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/users/4
content-type: application/json

### Listar todos os users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users
content-type: application/json



### Criar um lobby
POST http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

{
  "name": "Lobby Teste 2",
  "description": "Descrição do lobby",
  "minPlayers": 2,
  "maxPlayers": 6,
  "rounds": 5,
  "ante": 100
}

### Listar todos os lobbies
GET http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies

### Obter lobby por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/4

### Juntar-se a um lobby
POST http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/4/join
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenteste2}}


### Sair de um lobby
POST http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/1/leave
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar jogadores de um lobby
GET http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/4/players

### Obter host do lobby
GET http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/4/host

### Obter players de uma partida
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/3/players

### Obter detalhes de uma partida
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/3